| field             = [[Chemistry]], [[Sociology]], [[Mathematics]], [[Philosophy]]
| work_institution  = [[University of Liège]]
| alma_mater        = [[University of Liège]]<br>(PhD in Physical and Chemical Sciences, 1905)
